tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE consumer_feedback (
  feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  food_item_name VARCHAR(50),
  feedback_text TEXT,
  rating INT,
  timestamp TIMESTAMP
)
CREATE TABLE consumer_feedback (   id INT PRIMARY KEY,   feedback_text TEXT,   rating INT,   product_id INT,   timestamp TIMESTAMP )
CREATE TABLE bioengineered_food_items (   id INT PRIMARY KEY,   item_name VARCHAR(255),   ingredients TEXT,   country_of_origin VARCHAR(100),   nutrition_info TEXT )
CREATE TABLE product_development_strategies (   id INT PRIMARY KEY,   strategy_name VARCHAR(255),   target_audience VARCHAR(255),   implementation_plan TEXT,   budget DECIMAL(10,2) )
CREATE TABLE feedback_analysis_results (   id INT PRIMARY KEY,   feedback_id INT,   analysis_report TEXT,   recommendation TEXT,   analyst_id INT,   timestamp TIMESTAMP )
CREATE TABLE product_feedback_mapping (   id INT PRIMARY KEY,   product_id INT,   feedback_id INT,   mapping_status VARCHAR(50) )
